    <item>
      <title>最新民意调查显示，人们对南非未来的乐观情绪有所上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/optimism-about-south-africa-s-future-has-climbed-new-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查显示，受到商业友好型联合政府的组建以及连续六个月无停电的鼓舞，对国家未来持乐观态度的南非人数量增加了一倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/optimism-about-south-africa-s-future-has-climbed-new-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 13:52:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国总理敦促日本首相在紧张局势中保持两国关系稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/chinese-premier-urges-japan-pm-to-keep-ties-steady-amid-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强敦促日本首相石破茂在紧张局势中保持双边关系“健康、稳定”，并呼吁两国维护全球供应链和自由贸易的稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/chinese-premier-urges-japan-pm-to-keep-ties-steady-amid-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 13:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
